=head1 DESCRIPTION

The failover settings for the endpoint.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 EndpointErrorConditions => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The failover conditions for the endpoint. The options are:

=over

=item *

C<STALE_MANIFEST> - The manifest stalled and there are no new segments
or parts.

=item *

C<INCOMPLETE_MANIFEST> - There is a gap in the manifest.

=item *

C<MISSING_DRM_KEY> - Key rotation is enabled but we're unable to fetch
the key for the current key period.

=item *

C<SLATE_INPUT> - The segments which contain slate content are
considered to be missing content.

=back




